BRIEFLY 
Arthur Andersen in Soviet Union's Venture: Arthur Andersen &amp; Co. announced 
that the Soviet Union's Ministry of Finance approved a joint-venture agreement 
between Arthur Andersen &amp; Co. and two leading Soviet companies, making 
Andersen the first professional services organization of its kind to be 
authorized to audit balance sheets of Soviet companies and to do audits of 
Western/Soviet joint ventures in the Soviet Union. Andersen is the first 
Western professional services organization to have a controlling interest in a 
joint venture in the Soviet Union. 
